<summary><b>Q1: Total amount each customer spent? (Click to expand)</b></summary>

**Query:**
```sql
SELECT s.customer_id, SUM(m.price) AS total_sales
FROM sales s
JOIN menu m ON s.product_id = m.product_id
GROUP BY s.customer_id;
